---
title: Saucy Mexican Chicken & Veggie Fusilli with Extra Cheddar Cheese
description: Embark on a true culinary adventure, when Mexican flavours are introduced to our favourite Italian staple - pasta. Tex-Mex spices dance with chicken and colourful veggies, all hugged by a blanket layer of Cheddar cheese. It’s a pasta party that’ll have your taste buds performing a salsa!

*We’ve replaced the orecchiette in this recipe with fusilli due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
